{"id":41,"parent_id":31,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":41,"title":"Mark 10","subtitle":"","short_title":"Mark","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 10"],[".studySummary",["i","Jesus teaches the higher law of marriage—He blesses little children—Jesus counsels the rich young man, foretells His own death, and heals blind Bartimæus."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.1","order":"03.04.010.4957"},["b","1"],"And he arose from thence, and cometh into the coasts of Judæa by the farther side of Jordan: and the people resort unto him again; and, as he was wont, he taught them again."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.2","order":"03.04.010.4958"},["b","2"],"¶And the Pharisees came to him, and asked him, Is it lawful for a man to put away",["i","his"],"wife? tempting him."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.3","order":"03.04.010.4959"},["b","3"],"And he answered and said unto them, What did Moses command you?"],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.4","order":"03.04.010.4960"},["b","4"],"And they said, Moses suffered to write a bill of divorcement, and to put",["i","her"],"away."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.5","order":"03.04.010.4961"},["b","5"],"And Jesus answered and said unto them, For the hardness of your heart he wrote you this precept."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.6","order":"03.04.010.4962"},["b","6"],"But from the beginning of the creation God made them male and female."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.7","order":"03.04.010.4963"},["b","7"],"For this cause shall a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"man"],"leave his father and mother, and cleave to his",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"wife"],";"],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.8","order":"03.04.010.4964"},["b","8"],"And they twain shall be one flesh: so then they are no more twain, but one flesh."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.9","order":"03.04.010.4965"},["b","9"],"What therefore God hath",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"joined"],"together, let not man put",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"asunder"],"."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.10","order":"03.04.010.4966"},["b","10"],"And in the house his disciples asked him again of the same",["i","matter."]],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.11","order":"03.04.010.4967"},["b","11"],"And he saith unto them, Whosoever shall put away his wife, and marry another, committeth adultery against her."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.12","order":"03.04.010.4968"},["b","12"],"And if a woman shall put away her husband, and be married to another, she committeth adultery."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.13","order":"03.04.010.4969"},["b","13"],"¶And they brought young children to him, that he should touch them: and",["i","his"],"disciples rebuked those that brought",["i","them."]],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.14","order":"03.04.010.4970"},["b","14"],"But when Jesus saw",["i","it,"],"he was much displeased, and said unto them, Suffer the little",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"children"],"to come unto me, and forbid them not: for of such is the kingdom of God."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.15","order":"03.04.010.4971"},["b","15"],"Verily I say unto you, Whosoever shall not receive the kingdom of God as a little",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"child"],", he shall not enter therein."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.16","order":"03.04.010.4972"},["b","16"],"And he took them up in his arms, put",["i","his"],"hands upon them, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"blessed"],"them."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.17","order":"03.04.010.4973"},["b","17"],"¶And when he was gone forth into the way, there came one running, and kneeled to him, and asked him, Good Master, what shall I do that I may inherit eternal life?"],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.18","order":"03.04.010.4974"},["b","18"],"And Jesus said unto him, Why callest thou me good?",["i","there is"],"none",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"good"],"but one,",["i","that is,"],"God."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.19","order":"03.04.010.4975"},["b","19"],"Thou knowest the commandments, Do not commit",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"adultery"],", Do not",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_19b"},"kill"],", Do not",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_19c"},"steal"],", Do not bear false witness,",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_19d"},"Defraud"],"not,",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_19e"},"Honour"],"thy father and mother."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.20","order":"03.04.010.4976"},["b","20"],"And he answered and said unto him, Master, all these have I observed from my youth."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.21","order":"03.04.010.4977"},["b","21"],"Then Jesus beholding him loved him, and said unto him, One thing thou lackest: go thy way, sell whatsoever thou hast, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"give"],"to the poor, and thou shalt have treasure in heaven: and come, take up the cross, and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_21b"},"follow"],"me."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.22","order":"03.04.010.4978"},["b","22"],"And he was sad at that saying, and went away grieved: for he had great possessions."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.23","order":"03.04.010.4979"},["b","23"],"¶And Jesus looked round about, and saith unto his disciples, How hardly shall they that have riches enter into the kingdom of God!"],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.24","order":"03.04.010.4980"},["b","24"],"And the disciples were astonished at his words. But Jesus answereth again, and saith unto them, Children, how hard is it for them that",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_24a"},"trust"],"in",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_24b"},"riches"],"to enter into the kingdom of God!"],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.25","order":"03.04.010.4981"},["b","25"],"It is easier for a camel to go through the eye of a needle, than for a rich man to enter into the kingdom of God."],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.26","order":"03.04.010.4982"},["b","26"],"And they were astonished out of measure, saying among themselves, Who then can be saved?"],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.27","order":"03.04.010.4983"},["b","27"],"And Jesus looking upon them saith,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_27a"},"With"],"men",["i","it is"],"impossible, but not with God: for with God all things are",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_27b"},"possible"],"."],["div",{"id":"28","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.28","order":"03.04.010.4984"},["b","28"],"¶Then Peter began to say unto him, Lo, we have left all, and have followed thee."],["div",{"id":"29","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.29","order":"03.04.010.4985"},["b","29"],"And Jesus answered and said, Verily I say unto you, There is no man that hath left house, or brethren, or sisters, or father, or mother, or wife, or children, or lands, for my sake, and the gospel’s,"],["div",{"id":"30","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.30","order":"03.04.010.4986"},["b","30"],"But he shall receive an",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_30a"},"hundredfold"],"now in this time, houses, and brethren, and sisters, and mothers, and children, and lands, with persecutions; and in the world to come eternal life."],["div",{"id":"31","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.31","order":"03.04.010.4987"},["b","31"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_31a"},"But"],"many",["i","that are"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_31b"},"first"],"shall be last; and the last first."],["div",{"id":"32","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.32","order":"03.04.010.4988"},["b","32"],"¶And they were in the way going up to Jerusalem; and Jesus went before them: and they were amazed; and as they followed, they were afraid. And he took again the twelve, and began to tell them what things should happen unto him,"],["div",{"id":"33","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.33","order":"03.04.010.4989"},["b","33"],["i","Saying,"],"Behold, we go up to Jerusalem; and the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_33a"},"Son of man"],"shall be delivered unto the chief priests, and unto the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_33b"},"scribes"],"; and they shall condemn him to death, and shall deliver him to the Gentiles:"],["div",{"id":"34","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.34","order":"03.04.010.4990"},["b","34"],"And they shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_34a"},"mock"],"him, and shall scourge him, and shall spit upon him, and shall kill him: and the third day he shall",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_34b"},"rise"],"again."],["div",{"id":"35","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.35","order":"03.04.010.4991"},["b","35"],"¶And James and John, the sons of Zebedee, come unto him, saying, Master, we would that thou shouldest do for us whatsoever we shall desire."],["div",{"id":"36","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.36","order":"03.04.010.4992"},["b","36"],"And he said unto them, What would ye that I should do for you?"],["div",{"id":"37","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.37","order":"03.04.010.4993"},["b","37"],"They said unto him, Grant unto us that we may sit, one on thy right hand, and the other on thy left hand, in thy glory."],["div",{"id":"38","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.38","order":"03.04.010.4994"},["b","38"],"But Jesus said unto them, Ye know not what ye ask: can ye drink of the cup that I drink of? and be baptized with the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_38a"},"baptism"],"that I am baptized with?"],["div",{"id":"39","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.39","order":"03.04.010.4995"},["b","39"],"And they said unto him, We can. And Jesus said unto them, Ye shall indeed drink of the cup that I drink of; and with the baptism that I am baptized withal shall ye be baptized:"],["div",{"id":"40","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.40","order":"03.04.010.4996"},["b","40"],"But to sit on my right hand and on my left hand is not mine to give; but",["i","it shall be given to them"],"for whom it is prepared."],["div",{"id":"41","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.41","order":"03.04.010.4997"},["b","41"],"And when the ten heard",["i","it,"],"they began to be much displeased with James and John."],["div",{"id":"42","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.42","order":"03.04.010.4998"},["b","42"],"But Jesus called them",["i","to him,"],"and saith unto them, Ye know that they which are accounted to rule over the Gentiles exercise lordship over them; and their great ones exercise authority upon them."],["div",{"id":"43","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.43","order":"03.04.010.4999"},["b","43"],"But so shall it not be among you: but whosoever will be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_43a"},"great"],"among you, shall be your minister:"],["div",{"id":"44","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.44","order":"03.04.010.5000"},["b","44"],"And whosoever of you will be the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_44a"},"chiefest"],", shall be servant of all."],["div",{"id":"45","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.45","order":"03.04.010.5001"},["b","45"],"For even the Son of man came not to be ministered unto, but to minister, and to give his life a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_45a"},"ransom"],"for many."],["div",{"id":"46","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.46","order":"03.04.010.5002"},["b","46"],"¶And they came to Jericho: and as he went out of Jericho with his disciples and a great number of people, blind",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_46a"},"Bartimæus"],", the son of Timæus, sat by the highway side begging."],["div",{"id":"47","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.47","order":"03.04.010.5003"},["b","47"],"And when he heard that it was Jesus of Nazareth, he began to cry out, and say, Jesus,",["i","thou"],"Son of David, have mercy on me."],["div",{"id":"48","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.48","order":"03.04.010.5004"},["b","48"],"And many charged him that he should hold his peace: but he cried the more a great deal,",["i","Thou"],"Son of David, have mercy on me."],["div",{"id":"49","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.49","order":"03.04.010.5005"},["b","49"],"And Jesus stood still, and commanded him to be called. And they call the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_49a"},"blind"],"man, saying unto him, Be of good comfort, rise; he calleth thee."],["div",{"id":"50","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.50","order":"03.04.010.5006"},["b","50"],"And he, casting away his garment, rose, and came to Jesus."],["div",{"id":"51","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.51","order":"03.04.010.5007"},["b","51"],"And Jesus answered and said unto him, What wilt thou that I should do unto thee? The blind man said unto him, Lord, that I might receive my sight."],["div",{"id":"52","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.52","order":"03.04.010.5008"},["b","52"],"And Jesus said unto him, Go thy way; thy faith hath",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_52a"},"made thee whole"],". And immediately he received his sight, and followed Jesus in the way."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.7a","order":"03.04.010.5009"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/marriage-husbands"},"TG Marriage, Husbands"],"."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.7b","order":"03.04.010.5011"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/marriage-wives"},"TG Marriage, Wives"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.9a","order":"03.04.010.5013"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/family-eternal"},"TG Family, Eternal"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/genealogy-and-temple-work"},"Genealogy and Temple Work"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/marriage-marry"},"Marriage, Marry"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.9b","order":"03.04.010.5015"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/divorce"},"TG Divorce"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.14a","order":"03.04.010.5017"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/moro/8.8.5-9"},"Moro. 8:8 (5–9)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/example"},"TG Example"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.15a","order":"03.04.010.5019"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/meek"},"TG Meek"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.16a","order":"03.04.010.5021"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/17.21"},"3 Ne. 17:21"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/salvation-of-little-children"},"TG Salvation of Little Children"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.18a","order":"03.04.010.5023"},["b","18a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/ether/4.12.11-12"},"Ether 4:12 (11–12)"],"."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.19a","order":"03.04.010.5025"},["b","19a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/66.10"},"D&C 66:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"19b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.19b","order":"03.04.010.5027"},["b","19b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/murder"},"TG Murder"],"."],["div",{"id":"19c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.19c","order":"03.04.010.5029"},["b","19c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/stealing"},"TG Stealing"],"."],["div",{"id":"19d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.19d","order":"03.04.010.5031"},["b","19d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/fraud"},"TG Fraud"],"."],["div",{"id":"19e","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.19e","order":"03.04.010.5033"},["b","19e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/honoring-father-and-mother"},"TG Honoring Father and Mother"],"."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.21a","order":"03.04.010.5035"},["b","21a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/charity"},"TG Charity"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/generosity"},"Generosity"],"."],["div",{"id":"21b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.21b","order":"03.04.010.5037"},["b","21b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-exemplar"},"TG Jesus Christ, Exemplar"],"."],["div",{"id":"24a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.24a","order":"03.04.010.5039"},["b","24a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/2.18.17-19"},"Jacob 2:18 (17–19)"],"."],["div",{"id":"24b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.24b","order":"03.04.010.5041"},["b","24b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/treasure"},"TG Treasure"],"."],["div",{"id":"27a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.27a","order":"03.04.010.5043"},["b","27a"],["span.small","JST"],"Mark 10:26 … With men",["i","that trust in riches,"],"it is impossible; but not",["i","impossible with men who trust in God and leave all for my sake,"],"for with",["i","such"],"all",["i","these"],"things are possible."],["div",{"id":"27b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.27b","order":"03.04.010.5045"},["b","27b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-power-of"},"TG God, Power of"],"."],["div",{"id":"30a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.30a","order":"03.04.010.5047"},["b","30a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/reward"},"TG Reward"],"."],["div",{"id":"31a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.31a","order":"03.04.010.5049"},["b","31a"],["span.small","JST"],"Mark 10:30–31 But",["i","there are"],"many",["i","who make themselves"],"first,",["i","that"],"shall be last, and the last first.",["i","This he said, rebuking Peter"],"…"],["div",{"id":"31b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.31b","order":"03.04.010.5051"},["b","31b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/5.63"},"Jacob 5:63"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/ether/13.12.10-12"},"Ether 13:12 (10–12)"],"."],["div",{"id":"33a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.33a","order":"03.04.010.5053"},["b","33a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-son-of-man"},"TG Jesus Christ, Son of Man"],"."],["div",{"id":"33b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.33b","order":"03.04.010.5055"},["b","33b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/scribe"},"TG Scribe"],"."],["div",{"id":"34a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.34a","order":"03.04.010.5057"},["b","34a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/mocking"},"TG Mocking"],"."],["div",{"id":"34b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.34b","order":"03.04.010.5059"},["b","34b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-resurrection"},"TG Jesus Christ, Resurrection"],"."],["div",{"id":"38a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.38a","order":"03.04.010.5061"},["b","38a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-baptism-of"},"TG Jesus Christ, Baptism of"],"."],["div",{"id":"43a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.43a","order":"03.04.010.5063"},["b","43a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/50.26.26-27"},"D&C 50:26 (26–27)"],"."],["div",{"id":"44a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.44a","order":"03.04.010.5065"},["b","44a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/23.11"},"Matt. 23:11"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/22.24.24-30"},"Luke 22:24 (24–30)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/9.5"},"2 Ne. 9:5"],"."],["div",{"id":"45a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.45a","order":"03.04.010.5067"},["b","45a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/4.25"},"Rom. 4:25"],"."],["div",{"id":"46a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.46a","order":"03.04.010.5069"},["b","46a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/20.30.29-34"},"Matt. 20:30 (29–34)"],"."],["div",{"id":"49a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.49a","order":"03.04.010.5071"},["b","49a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/17.51"},"1 Ne. 17:51"],"."],["div",{"id":"52a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.52a","order":"03.04.010.5073"},["b","52a"],["span.small","GR"],"saved, preserved, healed thee."]]}
